00:55:48,420 --> 00:55:50,010
Homer Simpson.
荷马辛普森

1029
00:55:54,700 --> 00:55:56,990
If you can just turn down the voice,the sound a little bit,
能不能把声音调低一点

1030
00:55:57,170 --> 00:55:59,560
because this is very loud. Thank you.
因为它非常大声 谢谢

1031
00:55:59,230 --> 00:56:00,200
The Simpsons
辛普森一家

