00:56:02,860 --> 00:56:04,270
This is a simple lie detector.
这是一台简单的测谎仪

1035
00:56:04,500 --> 00:56:05,900
I'll ask you a few yes or no questions
我会问你几个问题 你回答是或否

1036
00:56:06,150 --> 00:56:07,550
and you just answer truthfully.
你要老实回答

